snippet.title: Starflight 3 - Prototype First Look
snippet.description:
Back us now on Fig!
https://fig.co/starflight3

Starflight Returns! From Greg Johnson, the creator of the legendary Starflight games comes the third installment in the series that defined the space RPG genre. Build your team, christen your ship, and explore a new part of the universe to cure a mysterious plague!
